          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1585752840788-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1585752840788-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Boil over a high heat for 4-5 min or until softened with a slight bite</p><p>Once softened, drain the <strong>noodles</strong>, run them under <strong>cold water</strong>, then return to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and set aside</p><p>Tip: The oil prevents the noodles from sticking together!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1585752844222-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1585752844222-x400.jpg",
