          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1585752844222-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel lengths off your <strong>courgette[s] </strong>until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> tamarind paste</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>mirin</strong>, <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and give it all a good mix up – this is your <strong>pad Thai sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1585752847708-x200.jpg",
