            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crush your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don’t have a rolling pin, just chop them roughly!</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil </strong>and <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1585752856906-x200.jpg",
