            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat and add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> along with the<strong> roasted butternut squash</strong> and <strong>pad Thai sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Stir through <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped basil</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) – this is your <strong>tangy</strong> <strong>vegetable pad Thai</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
