      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, sprinkle the<strong> remaining chopped basil </strong>and <strong>coriander</strong> and the <strong>crushed peanuts</strong> all over the <strong>tangy vegetable pad Thai</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
